				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I don't know where it comes from but I have found it isn't uncommon in some of the shops from time to time.  The best stuff can be found in places like East Freeport before people take off for a journey, or after they come back.  That's where I picked up mine.  I prefer to use it over the banded anyday because of the buffs it gives.  Just keep looking in your favorite shops and some that you don't go to.  You'll come across one.  I paid just over 1pp for it.  I think it is a Pally only item, and the one I'm wearing now is my second.  The first was given to me by a Dark Elf (of all races) who was fighting a young kodiak.  I jumped in and helped her, then had to lay hands just as she was dying.  It was a nice prize, and I tried to refuse, but she said it was for Paladins.  Anyway, if you find it, keep it.  It's worth the AC lost for the buffs it gives.
